The Vim password safe is written by Noah Spurrier
http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=2012

I wanted to add a small feature to it for my own use, but needed a place to
save it away where I could find it.

Noah has open sourced this code by releasing all copyright claim to it,
so I will do the same:

